examples.en: This apple tree is a poor yielder.
The apple trees were heavy with fruit.
These apple trees are not going to bear.
He propagated the apple tree by grafting.
The apple trees yielded an abundant harvest.
The apple trees are just beginning to blossom.
Mature apple trees are typically 20 feet tall.
examples.ru: Зрелые / взрослые / яблони, как правило, 20 футов в высоту.

examples.en: It was May, and the apple trees were all in flower.
examples.ru: Это было в мае, и все яблони были в цвету.

examples.en: The apple tree was bowed down with the weight of its fruit.
He retaliated his neighbor's malicious destruction of his flower garden by cutting down the man's prize apple tree.
examples.ru: Он отомстил соседу за умышленное уничтожение цветника, срубив его самую лучшую яблоню.
